name: Moshur Dal
dece: Deshi. These skinless, red lentils are small and round. They are fast-cooking and don't need to be soaked. They are often cooked, mashed and added to curries and soups.

name: Malta
dece: Malta, a variety of orange, is a popular citrus fruit cultivated in hot climate. The fruit is rich in mineral salts and other ingredients of nutritive value such as iron, lime, phosphorus, and vital minerals.Malta is loaded with vitamin C and vitamin B complex.
